01:01:57,651 --> 01:02:00,151
I shouldn't have told her about Lee Gyu Min.

787
01:02:04,825 --> 01:02:06,824
How can I help you?

788
01:02:08,294 --> 01:02:11,067
- Hey, hey, hey!
- You punk. Get up!

789
01:02:11,068 --> 01:02:12,755
- Hey!
- Come out!

790
01:02:12,756 --> 01:02:14,921
Come on!

791
01:02:14,921 --> 01:02:16,724
Let go of me. Let go.

792
01:02:16,725 --> 01:02:18,625
What's wrong with you?

793
01:02:29,031 --> 01:02:30,831
Seriously!

794
01:02:31,441 --> 01:02:34,067
Even if you are angry, you can't do that here.

795
01:02:34,068 --> 01:02:37,841
You could get charged for obstructing a public official's duty.

796
01:02:37,841 --> 01:02:41,320
I'm sorry. I'll talk to him.

797
01:02:41,320 --> 01:02:44,420
I'm sorry. Sorry.

798
01:02:47,219 --> 01:02:50,470
Why are you throwing a fit, too?

799
01:02:52,322 --> 01:02:55,422
I'll just get Yun Jin Ah out of there first, okay?

800
01:02:57,827 --> 01:03:00,127
Hey, you just stay here.

801
01:03:00,959 --> 01:03:03,959
Gosh, this guy is crazy.

802
01:03:07,834 --> 01:03:10,334
Don't do it, Jun Hui.

803
01:03:22,600 --> 01:03:28,410
♫ I feel you now from here ♫

804
01:03:29,260 --> 01:03:35,150
♫ Our time is not done yet ♫

805
01:03:35,990 --> 01:03:41,530
♫ You've given me my fullest heart ♫

806
01:03:42,130 --> 01:03:47,600
♫ We'll never be apart ♫

807
01:03:49,697 --> 01:03:53,596
You've gone through a lot of heartache since you started seeing me, right?

808
01:03:53,597 --> 01:03:56,617
Don't worry. I'll do better.

809
01:03:56,617 --> 01:03:58,546
There's something you aren't telling me, isn't there?

810
01:03:58,546 --> 01:04:01,476
Did you have fun in Gangwon-do with Jin Ah?

811
01:04:01,477 --> 01:04:03,877
It's the first I'm hearing about it.

812
01:04:05,800 --> 01:04:09,800
Whatever it is, I'm ready to hear it.

813
01:04:09,800 --> 01:04:11,614
Were you that worried about me?

814
01:04:11,615 --> 01:04:15,452
The fact that there's no legal problem has no meaning to us.

815
01:04:15,453 --> 01:04:17,169
Why does it have to be Yun Jin Ah?

816
01:04:17,169 --> 01:04:19,634
Because she's Yun Jin Ah.

817
01:04:19,634 --> 01:04:21,021
I'm sorry, Seung Ho.

818
01:04:21,022 --> 01:04:23,322
Hey, hey! Yun Jin Ah!

819
01:04:24,503 --> 01:04:26,604
I never thought...

820
01:04:27,272 --> 01:04:30,972
I would be so loved by someone.

821
01:04:31,767 --> 01:04:33,567
I love you...

822
01:04:34,467 --> 01:04:36,467
very much.

823
01:04:38,644 --> 01:04:42,944
I'll love you for a very long time.

824
01:04:42,944 --> 01:04:46,170
♫ I feel everything ♫

825
01:04:46,170 --> 01:04:51,380
♫ Never been so exposed... ♫
